Sazka May Be Sold in Tender, Administrator Tells Aktualne.cz

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-08-12T06:31:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-12/sazka-may-be-sold-in-tender-administrator-tells-aktualne-cz.html
Sazka AS’s creditors committee
agreed to sell the Czech lottery company in a tender, Sazka’s
administrator Josef Cupka told  Aktualne.cz  in an interview.  Each bidder for Sazka will have to pay a 500 million-koruna
($29.3 million) deposit and the price offered for the company
will the main criteria for choosing the new owner, Cupka told
Aktualne.  To contact the reporter on this story:
